      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented V&V history; version-controlled simulation scripts; reproducible build environment.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional license with documented release notes. Simulation scripts stored in version-controlled repository with tagged releases. Independent re-run by second analyst confirmed bit-reproducible results. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
