      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard manufactured-solution benchmarks for incompressible Navier-Stokes; convergence order confirmed.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has published code verification results for laminar and turbulent pipe flow manufactured solutions confirming second-order spatial convergence. Internal benchmark suite results reviewed and accepted. Satisfies MRL 2 requirement."
